{
  "stem": "188.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Six months after we were there, we were seen by somebody who got suspicious and who went to the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And there came a notice for Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Oosterfeld to please come to the gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They had some questions for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we knew that somebody had seen my brother, who was very dark haired, dark complexion, and looked anything but a little Aryan boy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we went under the guise of we were children from Rotterdam, and Rotterdam had been bombed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "While Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Oosterfeld was questioned, we were put-- his wife took us on the back of his bike-- her bicycle, and someone else helped her and got us out of there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Took us to another hiding place, to a safe house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Oosterfeld was questioned about the children in his house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And he said, these are refugees from Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And the way we had memorized the information about Rotterdam-- because I'd never been there-- was-- but I had played Monopoly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And the Dutch Monopoly had streets and certain areas from Rotterdam in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "So I always felt somebody asked me where did you live, I would have an answer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "It never came to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "But somehow, I felt a sense of security in that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Oosterfeld was told that he should bring the children that were in his house to the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They wanted to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And they let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "They let him go home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And we had left by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And he went-- after he had gone home, he went back to them and said, listen, I'm terribly sorry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I would like to comply with your request.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
